      What's New in Version 6.4.1235
    
ALL NEW EVENT: You’re invited to the annual Fishing Derby! Get your tackle box and fishing pole ready and catch the most fish! Collect Derby Points by crafting delicious recipes such as Catfish Jambalaya and Mint Caviar and you can win the PERMANENT Manx Cat Farm Hand! Win Gold in both stages and upgrade to the Fishin’ Cat Farm Hand! - We’ve also made improvements to Marie’s Order Board to reduce requirements!



